result.title: VoidShell codeNcode weekly individual contest
result.content:
Hello folks! Greetings from codeNcode. It's a pretty new platform given birth in this year. ( I think the introduction ends here :/ )

In this weeks' contest we set (2*12/3+1-5)^2-6 problems. :D Problem setters are nfssdq adurysk Nipuna_Samarasekara adkroxx arg_007 phoenix71 . They are some great thinkers in the country. For first time we have a sponsor and it is VoidShell, the shell that you people will fill. ( what they say ).

The contest will be held online at time on jul 25, 2016... (and maybe also 2017, 2018 ,2019....)

Placed 1st will get a laptop :D . Top 250 will get a t-shirt.

The contest will be held on this site . A warm welcome to all of you :D
